pageContext.claim: “So for 45 years, they couldn't get a deal. I got one in one day. I said, "We're going to put tariffs on and we're going to either have a deal or not. We agreed in one day." ”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has a tendency to claim his deals have eluded politicians for 45 (or 50) years, and that appears to be the case here. There is no basis to make this claim.
